 Some apparently healthy meals are worse for you than demonised junk foods from the likes of McDonald 's , Burger King and Pizza Express , researchers have found .
Asda 's Piri Piri Chicken Pasta Salad contains 46.5 g of fat -- two thirds of the recommended daily intake for an adult .
And a Pizza Express Classic Margherita pizza has 683 calories and 37.calorie with Cheese .